The paper focuses on representation learning and outlier detection, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with data mining (cs.DM), computer vision (cs.CV), and databases (cs.DB) since it involves processing and analyzing large amounts of data.
